寅.definition: 3rd earthly branch: 3-5 a.m., 1st solar month (4th February-5th March), year of the Tiger; ancient Chinese compass point: 60°

寅吃卯糧.definition: lit. eating away next year's food in advance; fig. to dip into the next month's check; live now, pay later

寅支卯糧.definition: see 寅吃卯糧|寅吃卯粮[yin2 chi1 mao3 liang2]

寅時.definition: 3-5 am (in the system of two-hour subdivisions used in former times)
